      a(name="creds")
      h2 External credentials
      p This field is not required, but it's useful if your devops.json is publicly viewable. A public devops.json can't contain sensitive information such as credentials, but these credentials are necessary for Gutsy to . To enter credentials into Gutsy, simply edit your project and toss some JSON in the credentials field.
